nodes.text: Dwarf vinocks were a type of winged creature with cream skin and black eyes. In 10 BBY, the crime lord Dryden Vos kept a dwarf vinock on display in a case in his study on board his yacht, the First Light.

A dwarf vinock first appeared in the 2018 Anthology series film, Solo: A Star Wars Story. They were first identified in the current canon in the video "Every Creature in the Star Wars Movies", which was released by the Star Wars Kids Youtube channel in 2019.
